metadata.name: DIZZY HALL
metadata.description:
Maybe you have been here before.
A place Where nothing lasts.
I have climbed stairs and got nowhere.
The doors that I have opened, behind which there was no room.
I have seen you go, but you had no face.
I feel dizzy,
There must be a way.


4000*3595 Pixels
Modeled in Rhino
Rendered in 3DsMax-VRay
